<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 904/95 of 25 April 1995 laying down detailed rules for the granting of private storage aid for long-keeping cheeses </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (E&Uuml;) nr 904/95, millega kehtestatakse pika valmimisajaga juustude eraladustusabi andmise &uuml;ksikasjalikud eeskirjad 25. aprill 1995 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 804/68 of 27 June 1968 on the common organization of the market in milk and milk products (1), as last amended by the Act of Accession of Austria, Finland and Sweden and by Regulation (EC) No 3290/94 (2), and in particular Articles 9 (3) and 28 thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 27. juuni 1968. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 804/68 piima- ja piimatooteturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (1) viimati muudetud Austria, Soome ja Rootsi &uuml;hinemisaktiga ning m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 3290/94, (2) eriti selle artikli 9 l&otilde;iget 3 ja artiklit 28, ning arvestades, et: </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Council Regulation (EEC) No 508/71 (3) provides that private storage aid may be granted for certain long-keeping cheeses where there is a serious imbalance of the market which may be eliminated or reduced by seasonal storage; </inglise>
<eesti> n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 508/71 (3) n&auml;hakse ette teatavate pika valmimisajaga juustude eraladustusabi andmine, kui turu t&otilde;sist tasakaalustamatust saaks hooajalise ladustamise abil &auml;ra hoida v&otilde;i v&auml;hendada; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the seasonal nature of Emmental and Gruy&egrave;re cheese production is aggravated by the fact that the seasonal trend in consumption of such cheeses is the opposite of their production; whereas, therefore, provision should be made for recourse to such storage in respect of a quantity corresponding to the difference between summer and winter production; </inglise>
<eesti> Emmentali ja Gruy&egrave;re juustude tootmise hooajalisust raskendab t&otilde;siasi, et nende juustude tarbimishooaeg on vastupidine kui tootmishooaeg; seet&otilde;ttu tuleks s&auml;testada k&otilde;nealuse ladustamise kasutamine koguste puhul, mis vastavad suvise ja talvise toodangu erinevusele; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the detailed rules of this measure should determine the maximum quantity to benefit from it as well as the duration of the contracts in relation to the real requirements of the market and the keeping qualities of the cheeses in question; whereas it is necessary to specify the terms of the storage contract so as to enable the identification of the cheese and to maintain checks on the stock in respect of which aid is granted; whereas the aid should be fixed taking into account storage costs and the foreseeable trend of market prices; </inglise>
<eesti> k&otilde;nealuse meetme &uuml;ksikasjalike eeskirjadega tuleks kindlaks m&auml;&auml;rata maksimumkogus, mille puhul abi antakse, ning lepingute kehtivusaeg vastavalt tegelikele turun&otilde;uetele ja k&otilde;nealuste juustude s&auml;ilivusele; on vaja t&auml;psustada laolepingute tingimused, mis v&otilde;imaldavad juuste kindlaks teha ning kontrollida ladusid, mille puhul abi antakse; abi tuleks kindlaks m&auml;&auml;rata, v&otilde;ttes arvesse laokulusid ja turuhindade prognoositavat suundumust; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in view of experience in controls, the provisions relating thereto should be specified, in particular as regards the documents to be presented and the on-the-spot checks to be conducted; whereas these new requirements on the subject make it necessary to stipulate that the Member States may provide that the costs of controls be fully or in part charged to the contractor; </inglise>
<eesti> pidades silmas kontrollimise kogemusi, tuleks t&auml;psustada seda k&auml;sitlevad s&auml;tted, eriti seoses esitatavate dokumentide ja kohapealsete kontrollidega; need uued n&otilde;uded eeldavad s&auml;tteid, mille kohaselt liikmesriigid v&otilde;ivad s&auml;testada, et kontrollide kulud kannab t&auml;ielikult v&otilde;i osaliselt lepingupool; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 1 (1) of Commission Regulation (EEC) No 1756/93 of 30 June 1993 fixing the operative events for the agricultural conversion rate applicable to milk and milk products (4), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 693/95 (5), fixes the conversion rate to be applied in the framework of private storage aid schemes in the milk products sector; </inglise>
<eesti> komisjoni 30. juuni 1993. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1756/93 (millega m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks piima ja piimatoodete p&otilde;llumajandusliku &uuml;mberarvestuskursi rakendusjuhud, (4) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 693/94 (5)) artikli 1 l&otilde;ikega 1 m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks piimasektoris eraladustamise abikava raames kohaldatav &uuml;mberarvestuskurss; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas it is appropriate to guarantee the continuation of the storage operations in question; </inglise>
<eesti> on vaja tagada k&otilde;nealuste ladustamistoimingute j&auml;tkumine; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for Milk and Milk Products, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las piima- ja piimatooteturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> Aid shall be granted in respect of the private storage of 19 900 tonnes of Emmental and Gruy&egrave;re cheeses manufactured in the Community which satisfy the requirements of Articles 2 and 3 hereof. </inglise>
<eesti> Abi antakse 19 900 tonni &uuml;henduses valmistatud ja artiklites 2 ja 3 esitatud n&otilde;uetele vastava Emmentali ja Gruy&egrave;re juustu eraladustamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
